# Concepts

Ongoing terminology hygiene for Pi Discord Threads.

## Rule

Project terms live in [Pi Discord Threads Glossary](../resources/pi-discord-threads-glossary.svx). This Area owns the standard for when a term graduates into the glossary.

Add a term when it prevents future mistakes in code, docs, tests, operations, or agent handoffs. Do not add generic programming vocabulary.

## Current canonical terms

- Pi session JSONL
- Registry projection
- Redis run control
- At-least-once run control
- Idempotent finalization
- XState lifecycle truth
- Effect resource seam
- LaunchAgent boundary
- Release snapshot
- `releases/current`
- Zero lost work + fast rollback

## Review cadence

Revisit this area after any slice that adds a durable state owner, lifecycle state, release/deploy concept, or public operator command.
